A Neon é uma fintech brasileira, fundada em 2016, que tem a missão de unir tecnologia e design para redesenhar e simplificar a experiência financeira das pessoas.

Com mais de 350 funcionários, a Neon levantou, em 2018, R$ 72 milhões de investimentos Series A em round liderado pela Propel Ventures, Monashees e Quona, que contou também com a Yellow Ventures, Omydiar Network e Tera Capital. Sendo a conta digital o principal produto, a fintech possui uma parceria com o Banco Votorantim para custódia e liquidação de suas contas.

rodrigo.salem@meifacil.com

Dedicated, striving and always chasing after new knowledge, with this profile I managed in just 1 year and a half to be the leadership of an international product, working in various stages that compose the product development (from the project to the manufacturing quality).
During all these years of experience, I have faced several challenges, some of this seemed bigger than what I could face and I ended up overcoming with a lot of effort, dedication and humbleness to listen to and to look for more experienced people. The patent development was challenging and at the beginning completely unknown to me. After a few months working with the team responsible for patents we elaborated a document praised by all. The implementation of a quality process in the electronics production was another great challenge, successfully overcame. At the beginning of the project I had almost no knowledge about electronics manufacture process and at the end we were able to implement quality process with a high success rate for a low current consumption product.
Developing product and coordinating tasks is always a challenge â€“ taking field trips, following up the manufacture process (in another state), meetings with all the teams, coordinating people. The job can be stressful, and to keep the balance at work it is important a personal balance: Sports (such as boxing and swimming), hanging out with family and friends, travelling with family, playing with the dog when I arrive from work, watching a film or tv shows are activities that help me to keep the balance and have a more efficient work rhythm.

experiencia_profissional.descricao: Disk Cook (the precursor and mother of iFood) was a high end full-service food delivery and logistic platform, where people ordered from the best restaurants in town and really tracked their order in real time using probably the coolest food delivery APP on market. Started as an offline channel (call center), Disk Cook became famous for displaying the best quality restaurants delivery system. It is responsible for creating and transferring most of its system and know-how to iFood. In 2014, iFood decided to buy its mother, transforming Disk Cook in a premium service offering exclusive restaurants focused on more demanding customers.

experiencia_profissional.cargo: Founder, M&A and Chairman of the Board
experiencia_profissional.descricao: iFood is the biggest online restaurant marketplace for food ordering in Latam and one of the biggest in the world. The concept was idealized inside Disk Cook in 2006, and launched in 2011 with the investment of Warehouse VC. In 2012, Movile Internet invested and joined the group. In 2013 iFood was already the marked leader in the country with a growth rate much higher than any other player. After creating and bootstrapping the company, as the M&A head, I was responsible to merge with Just-Eat and to acquire 5 other companies in the segment. iFood was transformed to become the biggest Latam player and one of the best operated delivery platforms in the world. For sure one of the first Brazilian Unicorn!

RapiDDo, acquired by iFood was a last mile logistic platform, concentrated on delivering documents or other goods in a very short time frame with real time tracking. It was created based on the know-how accumulated from the DiskCook dispatch and tracking system. The company is rapidly increasing and promises to change the SDD (Same Day Delivery) market.
